name: Party Animals
description:
Avalanche Party Animals is a collection of 10,000 unique, NFTs, who are
breaking the dance floor on the Avalanche Blockchain and canâ€™t wait to
finally enter the Party Animals Mansion. APA are based on the unofficial
Avalanche mascot, Wolfie. We hope to bring it to its rightful place as
the official mascot and by doing so, also bring recognition to the
platform. Each Party Animal is hand-drawn by our talented artist and is
randomly generated from numerous of assets. All of them are unique, but
some are simply legendary.
